<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Location - Global Azure Bootcamp 2018</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="@ViewBag.Location - Global Azure Bootcamp 2018">
    <meta property="og:image" content="~/images/fb_img.png">
    <environment names="Development,Staging,Production">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css" />

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/animate.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/slick.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/js/rs-plugin/css/settings.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/custom.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/TimeCircles.css" />
    </environment>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
                <div class="navbar-header">
                    <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1"> <span class="fa fa-bars fa-lg"></span> </button>
                    <a class="navbar-brand"> <img src="~/images/logo.png" alt="" class="logo"> </a>
                </div>
                <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                        <li>
                            <a href="#about">about</a>
                        </li>
                        @RenderSection("Menu", false)
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
            </div>
            <!-- /.container-->
        </nav>
        <div class="text-center intro">
            <div class="intro-body">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div id="divTimer">
                                <div id="CountDownTimer" data-bgcolor="#fff" data-date="2018-04-21 00:00:00" class="centered"
                                     style="width: 100%; height:auto; margin: 1em auto;" />
                            </div>
                            @RenderSection("Callout", false)
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="msRow">
            <div class="mslogo"></div>
            <div class="marketing-logo">
                <img src="~/images/logo-circle.png" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <section id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-heading scrollpoint sp-effect3">
                    <h1>Welcome</h1>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <p>On 21 April 2018, the Global Azure Bootcamp will be held once again with over 200 locations worldwide. This free community-run event aims to get you hands on experience developing and supporting Azure-based solutions while learning from local Azure experts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-6">
                        <div class="about-item scrollpoint sp-effect2">
                            <i class="fa fa-cloud fa-2x"></i>
                            <h3>Community Run</h3>
                            <p>Sessions will be delivered by local Microsoft MVPs and other Azure experts. Interact, ask questions, get help and learn.<br/><br /> 
                          </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-6">
                        <div class="about-item scrollpoint sp-effect5">
                            <i class="fa fa-usd fa-2x"></i>
                            <h3>Open to Everyone</h3>
                            <p>Entry to this event is totally free and open to anyone with basic to intermediate tech skills wanting to get more Azure experience.<br/><br/> <b>Just bring your own laptop.</b></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-6">
                        <div class="about-item scrollpoint sp-effect5">
                            <i class="fa fa-users fa-2x"></i>
                            <h3>Two Content Tracks</h3>
                            <p>Whether you're a developer wanting to build solutions on Azure or an IT administrator / engineer wanting to learn more about Azure's datacenter capabilities, there will be valuable content for you.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        @RenderBody()
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="large_white_light sft" data-x="center" data-y="250" data-hoffset="0" data-voffset="0" data-speed="1000" data-start="1400" data-easing="Power4.easeOut">
            [ Designed by
            <a href="//www.ganshani.com/?ref=azurebootcamp" target="_blank">Punit Ganshani</a> Update by
            <a href="//www.rramoscabral.com" target="_blank">Ricardo Cabral</a> Hosted on
            <a href="//azure.microsoft.com/en-us/" target="_blank">Microsoft Azure</a> Theme
            <a href="//www.scoopthemes.com/templates/Oleose/Freeze/" target="_blank">Freeze</a> ]
        </div>
    </footer>

   
    <environment names="Development,Staging,Production">
        <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
        <script src="~/lib/jquery-ui/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
        <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
        <!-- Animation JS -->
        <script src="~/js/slick.min.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
        <script src="~/js/placeholdem.min.js"></script>
        <script src="~/js/rs-plugin/js/jquery.themepunch.plugins.min.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
        <script src="~/js/rs-plugin/js/jquery.themepunch.revolution.min.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
        <script src="~/js/waypoints.min.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>

        <!--Custom JS-->

        <script src="~/js/TimeCircles.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
        <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
        <script src="~/js/custom.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>

    </environment>
    @RenderSection("scripts", required: false)
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            appMaster.preLoader();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>